<p>&#7902; &#273;&acirc;y b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7883;nh ngh&#297;a c&aacute;c th&#432; m&#7851;u (templates) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; g&#7917;i th&#432; t&#7899;i c&aacute;c danh s&aacute;ch. Th&#432; m&#7851;u l&agrave; m&#7897;t trang HTML c&oacute; h&#7897;p ch&#7913;a <b>[CONTENT]</b>. N&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a email s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&egrave;n v&agrave;o h&#7897;p ch&#7913;a n&agrave;y. </P>
<p>Ngo&agrave;i [CONTENT] ra, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&ecirc;m  [FOOTER] v&agrave; [SIGNATURE] &#273;&#7875; ch&egrave;n th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; ph&#7847;n &#273;u&ocirc;i (footer) v&agrave; ch&#7919; k&yacute; (signature), nh&#7919;ng h&#7897;p ch&#7913;a n&agrave;y l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c.</p>
<p>H&igrave;nh &#7843;nh trong  template s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i k&egrave;m v&#7899;i email. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&egrave;n h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh v&agrave;o n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a email (khi b&#7841;n g&#7917;i &#273;i), v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&oacute; d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; (complete URL), n&oacute; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng b&#7883; g&#7917;i k&egrave;m v&#7899;i email.</p>
<p><b>Gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t vi&#7879;c xem th&#432; c&#7911;a h&#7897;i vi&ecirc;n</b></p>
<p>&#272;&#7875; gi&uacute;p cho vi&#7879;c gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t h&#7897;i vi&ecirc;n, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&ecirc;m [USERID] v&agrave;o template, &#273;&#7883;nh danh c&#7911;a h&#7897;i vi&ecirc;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&egrave;n v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;. Ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng n&agrave;y ch&#7881; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i th&#432; c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng  l&agrave; HTML. B&#7841;n s&#7869; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p m&#7897;t s&#7889; trang n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n v&#7873; &#273;&#7883;nh danh ID c&#7911;a h&#7897;i vi&ecirc;n. C&oacute; m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c l&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; d&ugrave;ng ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng s&#7861;n l&agrave; <b>usertracking</b> c&#7911;a <?php echo NAME?>. &#272;&#7875; l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y b&#7841;n th&ecirc;m  [USERTRACK] v&agrave;o template v&agrave; m&#7897;t li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t &#7849;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o email &#273;&#7875; gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t vi&#7879;c m&#7903; th&#432; c&#7911;a h&#7897;i vi&ecirc;n.</p>
<p><b>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh</b></p>
<p>B&#7845;t k&#7923; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh d&ugrave;ng trong template m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; "http://" trong &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i t&#7843;i l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; g&#7917;i k&egrave;m v&agrave;o email. B&#7841;n ch&#7881; n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng &iacute;t h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh v&agrave; c&oacute; k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7887;. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n t&#7843;i l&ecirc;n  template, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; th&#7875; th&ecirc;m  h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh v&agrave;o. Tham chi&#7871;u t&#7899;i h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i k&egrave;m n&ecirc;n &#7903; d&#7841;ng c&ugrave;ng th&#432; m&#7909;c, v&iacute; d&#7909; l&agrave; &lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;image.jpg&quot;&nbsp;......&nbsp;&gt; ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&agrave; &lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;/some/directory/location/image.jpg&quot;&gt;</p>
